# Keep the build context small and free of secrets.
# NOTE: the build context is the PARENT of this repo (see Dockerfile), so these
# patterns are matched against `melon/...` and `felica-rs/...` too.
**/target/
**/.git/
**/.github/

# Secrets must never enter the image.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.jsonl
**/secrets/

# Not needed to build the server.
**/docs/
**/*.md
